<title>USA: RESEARCH ALERT - Mattson Tech started.</title>
<headline>RESEARCH ALERT - Mattson Tech started.</headline>
<text>
<p>-- Prudential Securities has started Mattson Technology Inc with a rating of hold, a source at the brokerage said on Friday.</p>
<p>-- Shares in the Fremont, Calif., manufacturer of fabrication equipment for semiconductor makers opened down 1/8 to 9-5/8.</p>
<p>((-- Wall Street desk (212) 859-1730))</p>
